Cliffe Crossing Phase II  is a multi Tenant Development over 8  acres that will build on the presence of the existing Phase I development located on the adjacent  corner. The new development supports a range of uses as well as space requirements. Targeted  Tenant Mix includes both local and national brand operations that support the local community area as well as destinations locations. Key design elements focus on easy access for customers visiting tenants with signage options to promote Tenants. See the Flyer for more information!

Cliffe Crossing is a multi Tenant Development over 5 acres including 3 buildings with ample parking . Current Tenant Mix includes both local and national brand operations. Key design elements were focused on easy access for customers visiting tenants. Also Large display windows and signage options to promote Tenant’ operations. See the Flyer for more information!

A key downtown location. Ground floor access with a patio area. The corner property is well situated for maximum street side exposure and provides excellent branding opportunities. Limited parking is available on site with ample parking available roadside and at the parking garage located across the street.
